item.title: CVE-2023-35056|2024-09-18T13:58:03.282Z -- yifan -- yf325
item.description: A buffer overflow vulnerability exists in the httpd next_page functionality of Yifan YF325 v1.0_20221108. A specially crafted network request can lead to command execution.
